| `--code-color-inline`     | Inline code color                          | `inherit`                   |
| `--code-font-family`      | Font family for all code elements          | `var(--font-family-mono)`   |
| `--code-font-size-inline` | Font size for inline `<code>` elements     | `inherit`                   |
