## Syntax Highlighting Theme Selection Tokens

Configure syntax highlighting theme presets or use custom CSS variables:

| Token               | Description                               | Default Value     |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------------------- | ----------------- |
| `--code-theme`      | Theme name for light mode or `custom`     | `basic-light`     |
| `--code-theme-dark` | Theme name for dark mode or `custom`      | `basic-dark`      |

